        "turn": 5,
        "name": "Act 2",
        "intent": "[The first room gives way to a harder one: the murmurs thin, the benches draw closer, and the air turns from accusation toward proof. A sealed stillness takes the place of certainty, as though the next door will not open for blame alone.]"
